data.description: This 4 bedroom/2 full bath Ranch style home is located in the Forrest Creek community and sits on a 0.37acre lot.  No HOA so you can easily park a boat or RV in the extra-large concrete driveway.  There is loads of parking space. Conveniently located but tucked away in the trees and quite private. There is a cute covered front porch where you can relax and enjoy a good book and a deck out back for your full enjoyment.   Beautifully remodeled and maintained with vaulted ceilings and all new LVP flooring, an open space living area, remodeled Master Bath and fresh paint.  The master bedroom is located at one end of home away from the other bedrooms.  A great home at a great price.  Call to schedule your private showing today!
